从google下载的google-chrome-stable.deb，安装后提示
adobe flash player is out of date

chrome://components

adobe flash player version 0.0.0.0

check for update

if it doesn't work, chrome://plugins  re-enable adobe flash

http://techdows.com/2015/07/fix-chrome-adobe-flash-player-was-blocked-because-it-is-out-of-date-error.html

now, pepper-flash is available on archlinux official repo,
and chromium remove chrome://plugins option,
you need enable it on chrome://settings/content/flash
when website notice you need to install flash, just click install and a window pop up ask you if allow to run flash on this website or not, just click yes, the flash will work.